svg.title: journey
svg.text: Set up fully immersive VR exhibits at entertainment conventions like SXSW & Comic-Con.
Bring in top ScreamFest filmmakers plus VR experts to film and produce on location for a highly intense and realistic experience.
For additional buzz, participants will be receiving video captures of their Virtual Reality reactions with sharable social media links.
Extending the experience, shared reactions are delivered to a microsite that features exclusive ticket and travel pack offers to users.
